Text: Post ID is RestoredPST Errol I would just like to let you know that Post ID has been restored Please give us a call if you have any questions Thank you Dan Original Message From Lim Francis S Sent Tuesday December PM To Arellano Fabian Dan Subject post id restore dan kindly continue the postid restore for erroll the directory is dumporaclearchives

FW Counterparty DunsLinkIDPST Sir We need the softcopy of the spreadsheet of counterparties which are to be moved to the Bankruptcy Book We would forward this to Kim so that she could fillup the list with the corresponding DunsLinkIDs Thank you Dan Original Message From Theriot Kim S Sent Monday December AM To Arellano Fabian Dan Subject RE Counterparty DunsLinkID I really need the spreadsheet that Errol provided to Francis before I can get started Francis that Errol provided him one spreadsheet and I would like to see that Kim Original Message From Arellano Fabian Dan Sent Monday December AM To Theriot Kim S Cc Lim Francis S Subject Counterparty DunsLinkID Hi Kim Im Dan Arellano and Im working with the TAGGERMS team under Francis Lim I am tasked by Francis to take care of the books to be moved to Bankruptcy Please forward to me the list of counterparties with their corresponding DunsLinkIDs andor Counterparty codes as soon as it is ready Thanks a lot Dan
